<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Festejando a Conexão do Campo à Cidade</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8edea, #fed6e3);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
          h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .images-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .image-box {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            width: 250px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .image-box img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .caption {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Celebrando a Conexão do Campo à Cidade</h1>
        <p>Unindo a beleza da natureza com a energia urbana!</p>
    </header>
    <div class="images-container">
        <div class="image-box">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506744038136-46273834b3fb?ixlib=rb-4.0.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Campo verde">
            <div class="caption">O verde do campo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-box">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494526585095-c4185f1cfae5?ixlib=rb-4.0.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Cidade iluminada">
            <div class="caption">A cidade vibrante</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
